modName: The Land of The Dead proof for TES Renewal Skyblivion (Very WIP)
summary: [WIP] Small-medium landscape mod located somewhere between Highrock's Farrun and Skyrim borders. Read description
descriptionHtml:
This is a new worldspace mod I made 4 years ago (maybe more) to be a full new quest worldspace mod with its own plot behind Skyrim. My 3D artist left because of free-time issues and we both abandoned the project. I'm uploading this as a PROOF to join Skyblivion.
There is no LOD done, and there is either any AI or enemies. Just the main mod's landscape.

INFO---The Plot
This was going to be located somewhere between Highrock's Farrun and Skyrim border. There is a celtic setup with a stonehenge, a lake surrounded by farms, an old fortress etc.
The main thing was to make a very immersive landscape, celtic-like themed with a nice history. 

TESTING IT--- How to get to the wolrdspace? (sorry, forgot to explain this)
coc 000intFarm1

IF YOU WANT TO USE IT
First of all, ask for permission as I inverted my time and passion making it. If you want to use this in any way, let me know, by Private Message. I do not give away this mod because, as I said before, it's a proof to join Skyblivion team. 
Thanks a lot for understanding
author: Sr_Gris
